Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  订货的时候搞错了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒是多出来几张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了 这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是买了Four season的最新专辑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了店铺购入特典的海报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在店里买的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有跟Four season毫无关系动画海报了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太震惊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明全国上下都是同样的特典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在日本国内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说佩里来了  可这不是美国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs15}（马休 佩里：日本历史上黑船事件中的美国海军将领  此事件就发生在夏色奇迹取景地的静冈县下田市）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  订货的时候对方似乎和别的歌手搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像刚才已经发货了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 明天下午就能到了  劳烦再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也搞地方歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京不会有这种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的话应该备货很足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且经常会有活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季真幸福啊  可以尽情去看现场演出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季要去东京的哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说之后会告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香也想去么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不只是去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为偶像么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以才想去东京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想陪在优香的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  明天还要你来陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs15}（优香  你的蛋蛋海报呢www）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已经没有贴的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（对不起  今天去不了了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,355)}（怎么了？）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(235,355)}（对不起  感冒了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子感冒了  现在正睡着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  所以才来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要睡一觉就能好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨你们要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和大家商量太鼓祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们家是执行委员会的成员嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  要扔下凛不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那么重的病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧也不是很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也说没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好了  就由我来照顾凛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心地睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不能和你一起去拿海报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个下次去拿就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想到一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向神石许愿治好凛的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一个人不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  叫上夏海和纱季吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒这种小病大家一起许愿的话很简单就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不会少块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不会少么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛这么说的话  今天就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我睡一会儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice 纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  我带了慰问品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是这里让人安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏期讲习很辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时欢迎来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问品超受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们都已经引退了 什么事都瞎操心有点不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说还记得么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春季大赛上赢了我们的稻中的柴田水野组合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢泽和水越
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想和那两个人打打看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和对方的部长联系过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时对方提出要打练习赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是在为了秋季大赛寻找调整状态的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说实际上我们很想上去打这场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是和她们说了「后辈会帮我们报仇的」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  让我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越  转学以后就没机会了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意输赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后你们俩就再打场比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈虽然那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然要打就一定要拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅野前辈她们输掉的时候  真的很不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然凭现在的实力还很困难…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来邮件了  是优香的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也发给夏海了哦  说凛感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有我陪着没问题的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反而让人更担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  就让她们两个独处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  人太多也很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又看到鲸鱼了吗  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会看到鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次得感冒都会看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头变得很晕  然后黑色的鲸就会咕噜噜地冒出来在我眼前游来游去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因为那个我们成为了好朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我还以为优香忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  环同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鲸在游来游去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的凛可是相当令人震惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海和纱季也还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个人出人意料地在这方面少根筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是代代木演唱会的蓝光碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  现在都没还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  这场演唱会你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了十遍  秋的个人舞蹈跳得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏在安可时唱错歌词了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有春在台阶上脚滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(253,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  能注意到那一点  真不愧是凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我稍微好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这样可不行  你明明在感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看  所以就来一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然凛这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说喊Call要适可而止  但是身体不由自主地动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,335)\fs16\fsp-2}オーイング
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs13}（オーイング: 指演唱会上在衔接副歌部分的间奏时,\N粉丝们随着节奏在台下“OH！OH！”大叫的行为。\N一般常见于脑残粉很多的偶像系演唱会）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（Four season… Four season… Four season…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论看几次都觉得好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说哪里厉害  看  就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对面秋和冬也一下子做出了一样的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  做得好像一开始就准备这么表演似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的团队精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就因为是她们四个人才能这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就因为是她们四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛喜欢的是春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是四个人都太喜欢了  所以就没有最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为春是最关心另外三个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(243,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些大大咧咧的 但是却最能关心另外三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像优香一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们练习舞蹈时  你都是练夏的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(393,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做冬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我做秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗感觉舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为夏一直都看着春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(302,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是在说她们的站位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们经常那样站位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天尽兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是有生以来最开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（对不起  今天我去不了了）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优香  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像优香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是什么可笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她是这么说的  但是她的嗓子都哑了  听上去很痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明俗话说笨蛋是不会得感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想去探病  结果她说「快好的时候是最关键的时候  一定不要过来」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊  因为探病而感冒再传回给你就太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子也一天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  今天接下来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  凛有什么想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卡拉OK吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  快来来来来  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今天没什么状态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为优香不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在的话就会变得很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为四个人一直都在一起  所以不曾意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少一个人就会变得这么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我要去别的地方  就在这里分开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  之前的海报送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君  把那张海报拿给她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  还有一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来确认一下海报是否送到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（特典海报送来了哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你病好了  一起去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个暂时是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是谢绝会面状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会转告她说你们来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来会拖很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不回我邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我四天没和优香见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  这种事已经几年没发生过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她在就会引起各种骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在心里埋怨「都是这家伙」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其实也是她非常努力地在为我们着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了她我们才能和好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小学四年级时转校过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始被大家觉得是有点奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是有分不清梦和现实的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鲸在游来游去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环同学是骗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子环 骗子环…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊  鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木也是骗子的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  男生们太吵了 没法学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她送到保健室去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我优香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫我凛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的看到了吧  鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是相信你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有一起看到的那一天就好了  那个鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  环同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我们一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为那件事我们成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊了之后发现大家都是Four season的歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时很流行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个人还在优香的家里练习舞蹈动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后四个人就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格虽然很不同  但是四个人在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还觉得只要我们四个人在一起就没有做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Four season一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到纱季去东京那天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要四个人更多地在一起  哪怕只多一天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是优香推荐的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香也一定是这样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你们一件事  一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向神石许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望优香的感冒能快点好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感冒拖一天就少一天和她在一起的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答应我一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事不要告诉优香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她也没什么吧  为什么不告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我得感冒的时候  我要优香别去向神石许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这样做太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  绝对不能想奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在天上飞什么的  想黏在一起什么的  想交换身体什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种绝对不能想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  这么说出来就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  我们再四个人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你们想要祈求希望我的感冒快点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很感激  但是太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我也已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  但是你姐姐说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了就是她说「传给客人就不好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就把我关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲得无聊  于是我就打手机游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果她说「不睡觉可不行」于是把我的手机没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才没法回邮件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你还真能想到我们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她告诉我你们来过了  所以我就想你们应该会在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  优香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是制止了你们真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们许愿的话一定又会发生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能像Four season那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看见了啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛的感冒已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  彻底地完全康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为是夏天就掉以轻心的话  又会得的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出回来后要漱口洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的病毒不光是冬季…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有睡眠不足也是禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想调理身体基本上也要靠睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  那里有个最好休息一下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.57,0:24:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇迹  第六话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的双打
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是家务又是社团活动又是作业
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海有好好睡觉吗
